 | direction = vertical
 | width = 200
 | footer = PMV / PPD方法的熱舒適性的兩種表示方式
 | image1 = Psychrometric chart - PMV method.png
 | caption1 = 溫度濕度表
 | image2 = Temperature-relative humidity chart - PMV method.png
